snippet.title: Sophia the Traveler. Demo Gameplay
snippet.description:
By Memo Gogo / Thermite Games. 2022.
Join our lovely heroine as she roams Venice the City of Water. Like a WheresWally Visual Novel: Search for objects & characters in stunning and vivid handpainted cityscapes!
